"""ribosome-dash — Live dashboard for ribosome task queue.

Reads ribosome.jsonl in real-time (tail -f style). Shows live updating table:
per-provider active/completed/failed/rate-limited counts, rolling success rate,
per-task progress with elapsed time, drain progress bar, ETA to queue drain.
Uses rich for terminal UI.

Usage:
    ribosome-dash              # Show live dashboard (auto-refresh)
    ribosome-dash --once       # Single snapshot, no live refresh
    ribosome-dash --window 60  # Rolling window in minutes (default 60)
"""

